This project includes code from the following projects, also released
under the ISC license:

Wallops - IRC client for classic Macintosh
Copyright (c) 2022-2026 joshua stein <jcs@jcs.org>
https://github.com/jcs/wallops

  Files derived from wallops:
  - src/tcp.c, src/tcp.h (MacTCP wrapper)
  - src/dnr.c, src/dnr.h (DNS resolution)
  - src/util.c, src/util.h (utility functions)
  - include/MacTCP.h (MacTCP headers)

Subtext - BBS server for classic Macintosh
Copyright (c) 2021-2022 joshua stein <jcs@jcs.org>
https://github.com/jcs/subtext

  Reference for telnet protocol implementation (adapted from
  server-side to client-side).

Some files also contain code with additional copyright holders:
- src/tcp.c: Copyright (c) 1990-1992 University of Illinois Board of Trustees
- src/dnr.c: Copyright Apple Computer, Inc. 1988
- src/util.c: Copyright (c) 1998, 2015 Todd C. Miller <millert@openbsd.org>;
